premise_source_doc_sentence: Charles University , known also as Charles University in Prague  (  Univerzita Karlova Universitas Carolina Karls-Universität  )  or historically as the University of Prague  (  Universitas Pragensis  )  , is the oldest and largest university in the Czech Republic .
